snippet.title: Outward: The Three Brothers Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
There is more than destruction on the path of an adventurer, the time for rebuilding has come! 

Outward: The Three Brothers is Out Now on PC! Console version to follow early 2021

DeepSilver: https://www.deepsilver.com/en/games/outward/         
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1437000/Outward_The_Three_Brothers/         
Twitter: @Outwardgame         
Instagram: @Outwardgame
      
Filled with new adventures, skills, weapons, recipes and pets, “The Three Brothers”-DLC offers you an entirely new journey in the unique world of Aurai!  

#Outward #Thethreebrothers #DLC
